{"title_page": "South African National Department of Health", "text_new": "{{Infobox Government agency\n|agency_name   = Department of Health\n|nativename    = {{collapsible list\n  |titlestyle = background:transparent;text-align:left;padding-left:2.5em;font-size:85%;<!--size of [show]/[hide] link-->\n  |liststyle = text-align:center;white-space:nowrap;\n  | {{small|{{nobold|''10 other official names:''}}}}\n  | {{native name|af|{{small|Departement van Gesondheid}}|fontsize=68%}}\n  | {{native name|nr|{{small|umNyango wezamaPhilo}}|fontsize=68%}}\n  | {{native name|xh|{{small|iSebe lezeMpilo}}|fontsize=68%}}\n  | {{native name|zu|{{small|uMyango Wezempilo}}|fontsize=68%}}\n  | {{native name|ss|{{small|Litiko Letemphilo}}|fontsize=68%}}\n  | {{native name|nso|{{small|Kgoro ya Maphelo}}|fontsize=68%}}\n  | {{native name|st|{{small|Lefapha la Bophelo bo Botle}}|fontsize=68%}}\n  | {{native name|tn|{{small|Lefapha la Pholo}}|fontsize=68%}}\n  | {{native name|ts|{{small|Ndzawulo ya Rihanyo}}|fontsize=68%}}\n  | {{native name|ve|{{small|Muhasho wa Mutakalo}}|fontsize=68%}}\n }}\n|formed        = \n|jurisdiction  = [[Government of South Africa]]\n|region_code   = ZA\n|budget        = \n|minister1_name  = [[Zweli Mkhize]]\n|minister1_pfo   = Minister of Health\n|minister2_name  = [[Joe Phaahla]]\n|minister2_pfo   = Deputy Minister of Health \n|chief1_name     = \n|chief1_position = Director-General: Health\n|type   = Department\n|website       = {{URL|www.doh.gov.za}}\n}}\n\nThe '''Department of Health''' is the executive department of the [[South Africa]]n government that is assigned to health matters. \n\nThe Office for Health Standards and Compliance was established in 2014.<ref>{{cite book|last1=Britnell|first1=Mark|title=In Search of the Perfect Health System|date=2015|publisher=Palgrave|location=London|isbn=978-1-137-49661-4|page=76}}</ref>\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n*[http://www.doh.gov.za/ Department of Health]\n\n{{SA Government departmen