| 2021\n| ''[[The Matrix 4]]''\n| style=\"background: PowderBlue; text-align: center\" | Lana only\n| style=\"background: PowderBlue; text-align: center\" | Lana only\n| style=\"background: PowderBlue; text-align: center\" | Lana only\n|\n|-\n|}\n\n=== Television ===\n\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n! rowspan=\"2\" | Year\n! rowspan=\"2\" | Title\n! colspan=\"3\" | Functioned as\n!\n! rowspan=\"2\" | Notes\n|-\n! [[Television program creators|Creators]]\n! [[Showrunner]]s\n! Writers\n! Directors\n|-\n| 2015\u20132018\n| ''[[Sense8]]''\n| {{yes}}\n| style=\"background: PowderBlue; text-align: center\" | Season 1: The Wachowskis<br />Season 2: Lana only\n| style=\"background: PowderBlue; text-align: center\" | Season 1: The Wachowskis<br />Season 2: Lana only\n| style=\"background: PowderBlue; text-align: center\" | Season 1: The Wachowskis<br />Season 2: Lana only\n| Co-created with [[J. Michael Straczynski]]<ref name=\"LillyBreak\" />\n|-\n| 2019\u2013present\n| ''[[Work in Progress (TV series)|Work in Progress]]''\n| {{no}}\n| style=\"background: PowderBlue; text-align: center\" | Lilly only\n| style=\"background: PowderBlue; text-align: center\" | Lilly only\n| {{no}}\n| \n|}\n\n=== Video games ===\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n! rowspan=\"2\" | Year\n! rowspan=\"2\" | Title\n! colspan=\"2\" | Functioned as\n! rowspan=\"2\" | Notes\n|-\n! [[Video game creative director|Directors]]\n! [[Screenwriter#Video game writing|Writers]]\n|-\n|2003\n| ''[[Enter the Matrix]]''\n| {{yes}}\n| {{yes}}\n|<ref>{{cite news|author=Marriott, Michel|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2003/02/20/technology/from-projector-to-polygons-a-thin-line-between-film-and-joystick.html?pagewanted=all&src=pm|title=From Projector to Polygons; A Thin Line Between Film And Joystick|work=The New York Times|date=February 20, 2003|accessdate=December 28, 2012|url-status=live|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140310222715/http://www.nytimes.com/2003/02/20/technology/from-projector-to-polygons-a-thin-line-be